headline: Stock Market Today: Dow Climbs 664 Points, Revisits 47,000; Nvidia Falls As Palantir Rises (Live Coverage)
summary: The Dow Jones Industrial Average and other major indexes ended Tuesday with hefty gains, as investors saw weak economic data as supporting a decision by the Federal Reserve to lower interest rates in December.
